Privacy Policy
Privacy Notice for MBC.net and Social Media
MBC is aware of the importance of privacy and protection of personal data at the digital era and is therefore committed to the protection of the privacy of the users of the MBC services while browsing or using our websites and using our services.
This privacy notice ("Privacy Notice") will describe how MBC ensures an adequate level of protection of personal data (i.e., any information relating to natural persons who can be identified, directly or indirectly, in particular by reference to an identifier such as a name, an identification number, location data, an online identifier or to one or more factors specific to that natural person; hereinafter "Personal Data").
More specifically, this Privacy Notice will describe:
1.  Who are we?
2.  What personal data do we collect about you?
3.  How do we collect your personal data?
4.  Why do we collect and process your Personal Data?
5.  On what legal basis do we process your Personal Data?
6.  Who may access your Personal Data?
7.  Where may your Personal Data be stored or transferred?
8.  How do we ensure the security of your Personal Data?
9.  How long do we store your Personal Data?
10.  Do we collect personal data from minors?
11.  What rights do you have?
12.  How do we use cookies?
13.  How does this Notice work with third-party data processing?
14.  How to contact us?
15.  How may this Privacy Notice be updated?
This Privacy Notice applies to all services offered and served by MBC FZ LLC on its websites, digital applications, competitions, social media platforms and other digital properties (
our Services
").
Further privacy notices, highlighting certain uses we wish to make of your Personal Data, together with the ability to opt in or out of selected uses may also be provided on a case-by-case basis, including for new or other services that might have separate privacy notice.
Under the data protection legislations, we are required to provide you with the information included in this privacy notice. It is important that you read this notice, together with any other notices that we may provide to you when collecting and processing your personal data.
Privacy Notice key definitions:
• "I", "our", "us", or "we" refer to MBC FZ LCC.
• "You", "the user" refer to the person(s) using the services of MBC and MBC’s social media platforms.
• "Social Media Platforms" refer to the social networks (Facebook, Twitter), the media sharing sites (Instagram, Snapchat, Youtube, Tiktok, Dailymotion) and social media messaging applications (WhatsApp, Telegram) used by the MBC.
