MBC Media KSA LLC, a limited liability company registered in Riyadh, Kingdom of Saudi Arabia with its registered office at Building Number 323Al Assafarat District 6501 - Samhah Street Postal Code 12511 – Riyadh, Saudi Arabia, processes your personal data while you use its websites and/or digital services and social media platforms.
MBC serves users in many different countries. The digital applications, competitions and other digital properties and online services (Services) are operated and maintained by MBC FZ LLC, a limited company registered in Dubai, UAE.
